In a 65 conversion forgot the flasher -- fried it.  I a 52-53?? ford 
missed two relays.  one fried and we found it by smell.  recommend 
changing them.  BTW Didnt notice if you had carbs.  The chokes will need 
to be replaced or a resistor mounted.
